| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4728 — Recovery Inhibition (blackshrantac)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 445c7fb7-d97e-5a7f-901c-ea4baf1bc346"
